---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Research"
  description="Scientific research projects based on ADS-B and Mode-S data collected by the FlyItalyADSB network: upper-troposphere wind measurement, ERA5 validation."
>
  <div class="pt-24 pb-20 px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

    <div class="mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Research</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-4">Scientific research</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        ADS-B and Mode-S data collected by the FlyItalyADSB network are used for meteorological
        and aeronautical research. Commercial aircraft in flight are distributed sensors at altitude:
        they allow wind, temperature and pressure to be measured with a spatiotemporal density
        impossible to achieve with traditional ground stations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Main project</p>
      <a href="/en/ricerca/weather" class="block p-8 rounded-2xl border no-underline group transition-all hover:border-sky-400/30"
         style="background:#0f1929;border-color:#1e3048">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium" style="background:#38bdf815;color:#7dd3fc;border:1px solid #38bdf830">Meteorology</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium" style="background:#10b98115;color:#34d399;border:1px solid #10b98130">Ongoing</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Upper-troposphere wind measurement from aircraft in flight
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl">
              Extraction of wind components (u, v) from Mode-S BDS50/BDS60 and ADS-B messages.
              True Air Speed (TAS) and magnetic heading are subtracted from ground speed (GPS track)
              to derive local wind. Results are validated against ERA5 reanalysis (ECMWF)
              and vertical profiles from IASI (MetOp satellite).
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6">
              {[
                { label: 'Data source', value: 'ADS-B + Mode-S BDS50/60' },
                { label: 'Validation', value: 'ERA5 · IASI (MetOp)' },
                { label: 'RMSE (u)', value: '7.38 m/s vs ERA5' },
              ].map(item => (
                <div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">{item.label}</div>
                  <div class="text-slate-300 text-xs font-mono">{item.value}</div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5" class="opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
              <path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 rounded-xl p-8 border" style="background:#0a1320;border-color:#1e3048">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0" style="background:#38bdf815;border:1px solid #38bdf830">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-100 mb-2">Data access for researchers</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Historical ADS-B datasets, MLAT CSV files and raw Mode-S data are not distributed publicly,
            but are available for university or institutional research upon request.
            Contact us with a brief description of your project and institution.
          </p>
          <a href="/en/chi-siamo#contatti"
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium no-underline transition-all"
             style="background:#38bdf815;color:#7dd3fc;border:1px solid #38bdf830"
             onmouseover="this.style.background='#38bdf825'"
             onmouseout="this.style.background='#38bdf815'">
            Request access →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
